      "text": "いいけど、今日はオフだから\nどこか寄って帰ろうと思ってるの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sure‚ but today is my day off\nso‚ I'm thinking of stopping by somewhere",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.813038683,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
