      "text": "じゃあ一緒に遊べるね！　芽衣もオフなんだ～\nどこ行く？　CDショップ？　映画館もいいな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ we can hang out together! It's Mei's day off‚ too~\nWhere should we go? CD shop? Also like Movie theater~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.955465587,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
