      "text": "そうね、今日はのんびりしたい気分だから\nカフェとかどうかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I'm in the mood to relax today\nHow about a cafe?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.6535151642,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
